    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/9df0ef393fbe28b01a981f64182b1a63.avif?t=1729108236\" width=600 height=85 /></span>欢迎来到Sugar Shack！这款游戏设定在一个似乎永远是春天的世界里，其中这个出产优质枫糖的舒适小屋全由你管理。点炉子，犁地，提取枫树液，恢复小屋周围的土壤活力。迎客、卖产品、烘焙自制小吃营造社区感，通过这些手段来提升小屋的声誉。把生机和欢乐带到新的奇幻世界——靠你自己或者跟朋友一起！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/db9894f32d1ae850b8665322576d013b.avif?t=1729108236\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/90fe915537a481d030a05474bbbb4926.poster.avif?t=1729108236\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/90fe915537a481d030a05474bbbb4926.webm?t=1729108236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/90fe915537a481d030a05474bbbb4926.mp4?t=1729108236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 没错，整个地图都可以自定义： 这意味着你可以选择邻居的位置、资源，甚至河流的流向！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你可以随意根据自己的喜好创建徒步路径、设置围栏和添加箱子，从而装饰你的地图。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每新放一格，都会带来丰富的活动！从而解锁新的任务、资源和机会。没有两个世界是一样的，所以可以无尽实验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/56c5b1f777c8e45e545f525158fe010f.avif?t=1729108236\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/71e6885df7551c9f5a4c138f1d545b94.poster.avif?t=1729108236\" width=612 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/71e6885df7551c9f5a4c138f1d545b94.webm?t=1729108236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/71e6885df7551c9f5a4c138f1d545b94.mp4?t=1729108236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sugar Shack充满了魁北克丰富的民间传说，在这里你可以按自己的节奏，享受轻松舒适的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 出去提取枫树液，摘莓果，照料花园。或者待在屋里做饭，接待本地人，帮忙解决他们的需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 甚至你还可以自定义场景，放置物品，创建自己的空间！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/ecdad624f97df1fd1f7c884d2c09dd74.avif?t=1729108236\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/053809bc3708860c83044c268e47e10a.poster.avif?t=1729108236\" width=612 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/053809bc3708860c83044c268e47e10a.webm?t=1729108236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/053809bc3708860c83044c268e47e10a.mp4?t=1729108236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 跟1-4个朋友一起建设这个世界：收集资源，分摊任务和收益。设计个性化房间，展示你的舒适风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 跟朋友一起服务客户，使这座小屋大获成功</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813130/extras/1b8a939ebd282fb3cb530c7e47a722e7.avif?t=1729108236\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你可以充分体验糖果屋中经典甜点的制作过程，如枫糖浆、枫糖太妃糖甚至海狸尾糕点！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏里的任务和 NPC 取材于诸如“飞翔的独木舟”、“拉科里沃”等魁北克民间传说。 认识这些多彩故事中的人物，了解他们的故事！</p></li></ul>",
